        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[【🤧#医生建议咳嗽打喷嚏养成1个习惯#】秋冬季节，呼吸道传染病高发，飞沫传播和接触传播是主要的传播途径。[话筒]医生提醒，#咳嗽打喷嚏时注意遮挡可保护周围...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【🤧<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E5%92%B3%E5%97%BD%E6%89%93%E5%96%B7%E5%9A%8F%E5%85%BB%E6%88%901%E4%B8%AA%E4%B9%A0%E6%83%AF%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E5%92%B3%E5%97%BD%E6%89%93%E5%96%B7%E5%9A%8F%E5%85%BB%E6%88%901%E4%B8%AA%E4%B9%A0%E6%83%AF%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#医生建议咳嗽打喷嚏养成1个习惯#</span></a>】秋冬季节，呼吸道传染病高发，飞沫传播和接触传播是主要的传播途径。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>医生提醒，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%92%B3%E5%97%BD%E6%89%93%E5%96%B7%E5%9A%8F%E6%97%B6%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E9%81%AE%E6%8C%A1%E5%8F%AF%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E5%91%A8%E5%9B%B4%E4%BA%BA%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%92%B3%E5%97%BD%E6%89%93%E5%96%B7%E5%9A%8F%E6%97%B6%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E9%81%AE%E6%8C%A1%E5%8F%AF%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E5%91%A8%E5%9B%B4%E4%BA%BA%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#咳嗽打喷嚏时注意遮挡可保护周围人#</span></a>。一旦明确自己感染，乘坐公共交通或就诊时戴好口罩，养成勤洗手等卫生习惯；咳嗽或打喷嚏时应注意用手帕、纸巾或胳膊肘遮挡口鼻，不要直接用双手，避免污染双手而将病毒等传播到他处👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视新闻）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4972800914685963" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hk9zhtd4qjj60bq0fmjw002.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.