            <title><![CDATA[#5个体检项目千万别躲着不做#[awsl]体检是早期发现疾病的最重要的途径！但很多人却因为种种原因，“躲”开一些项目，很多重大疾病可能会被遗漏。这5个项目，千万...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%235%E4%B8%AA%E4%BD%93%E6%A3%80%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%8D%83%E4%B8%87%E5%88%AB%E8%BA%B2%E7%9D%80%E4%B8%8D%E5%81%9A%23&amp;extparam=%235%E4%B8%AA%E4%BD%93%E6%A3%80%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%8D%83%E4%B8%87%E5%88%AB%E8%BA%B2%E7%9D%80%E4%B8%8D%E5%81%9A%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#5个体检项目千万别躲着不做#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[awsl]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/fb_a3awsl-ed1a33c1b3.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>体检是早期发现疾病的最重要的途径！但很多人却因为种种原因，“躲”开一些项目，很多重大疾病可能会被遗漏。这5个项目，千万别躲👇🏻<br><br>✅肛门指诊：能及时发现痔疮、肠癌等；<br>✅尿常规、粪常规：发现肾、泌尿系统、消化道疾病；<br>✅妇科检查：各种妇科疾病；<br>✅乳腺彩超：预防乳腺病变；<br>✅胃镜：检查胃部疾病。<br><br><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>最后卫子建议大家把近些年的体检报告妥善保存，方便观察身体指标的变化。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[奥特曼]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_aoteman-7ddbc90d1c.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫来辟谣#</span></a>（健康广东）<img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hkalkgv15sj20u00p4dik.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
